<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <!-- Grab title from the page data and dump it here -->
        <title>{{ title }}</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
        <link rel="icon" href="/assets/favicon.png" type="image/png">
        {% block og %}
            <meta property="og:title" content="Speed Patterns">
            <meta property="og:image" content="/assets/speed_patterns_og_image.png">
            <meta property="og:site_name" content="Speed Patterns">
        {% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body {% if id %} id="{{id}}"{%endif%}>

        <header>
            <span>
                <img class="logo" src="/assets/no_spinners_animated.svg" width="70" alt="no spinner logo">
                <a href="/">Speed Patterns</a>
            </span>
            <span>
                <a href="https://github.com/Speed-Patterns/speed-patterns"><img class="githublink" src="/assets/octocat_github_link_image_white_sized.svg" width="70" alt="octocat github link"></a>
                <img class="burger" src="/assets/speed_patterns_burger_menu.svg" width="60" alt="burger menu">
            </span>
        </header>

        <script>
            document
                .querySelector(".burger")
                .addEventListener("click", function () {
                    document
                        .querySelector("nav")
                        .classList
                        .toggle("mobile-hidden")
                })
        </script>

        <nav class="mobile-hidden">
            <ul>
                <li class="home-link">
                    <a href="/">
                        Home
                    </a>
                </li>
                {% for post in collections.pattern %}

                    <li>
                        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                    </li>

                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <main>
            {% block title %}{% endblock %}
            {{ content | safe }}
        </main>

        <aside class="sidebar">
            <p>
                <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/"><img alt="Creative Commons License" style="border-width:0" src="https://i.creativecommons.org/l/by/4.0/88x31.png"/></a><br/>This work is licensed under a <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License</a>.
            </p>

            <h3>Links</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://github.com/Speed-Patterns/speed-patterns">Our repo on GitHub</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://github.com/Speed-Patterns/speed-patterns/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md">Contribution Guide</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://github.com/Speed-Patterns/speed-patterns/issues">Issue tracker</a>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Sister sites</h3>
            <p>Some sites to help you with your preforamance adventure:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://wpostats.com/">WPO Stats</a> - collection of useful white papers with effect of speed on business KPIs</li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://whatdoesmysitecost.com/">What Does My Site Cost?</a> - tool to estimate the cost for the user loading your pages</li>
                <li>
                    <a href="http://www.slownesskills.com/">Slowness Kills</a> - helps your motivation if money is not enough of the motivator</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Even more links</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="http://www.perfplanet.com/">PerfPlanet</a> - blog aggregator from performance-related bloggers</li>
                <li>
                    <a href="http://calendar.perfplanet.com/">PerfPlanet Calendar</a> - collection of articles about web performance in PerfPlanet's advent calendars for almost a decade</li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://www.pinterest.com/perfplanet/">PerfPlanet Pinterest</a> - collection of books, inforgraphics and other speed-related info</li>
                <li>
                    <a href="http://www.webpagetest.org/">WebPageTest</a> - best tool for performance analysis</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Contributors</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://www.sergeychernyshev.com/">Sergey Chernyshev</a>
                </li>
                <li>... add your name <a href="https://github.com/Speed-Patterns/speed-patterns/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md">here</a>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Attribution</h3>
            <p>Theme built by <a href="https://www.alexchernyshev.com/">Alexander Chernyshev</a> using <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/">11ty</a>.
            </p>

        </aside>
    </body>
</html>